})}</script>

<script type="application/ld+json">{JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    { "@type": "Question", "name": "What is the median house price in Indooroopilly Brisbane?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Indooroopilly's median house price sits around $1.6 million as of early 2026, with annual growth around 7.5% and around 130 houses sold per year. Pricing varies considerably between renovated character homes, post-war family homes, and apartments around the centre. An appraisal will give you a precise read on where your property sits." } },
